text: Jennifer Odessa Nettles (born September 12, 1974) is an American country musician. She is the lead singer of the country group Sugarland. Nettles' first solo album, That Girl, was released on January 14, 2014.http://bostonherald.com/entertainment/music/music_news/2013/11/jennifer_nettles_talks_new_solo_album_motherhood Nettles was born in Douglas, Georgia. ==References== Category:Country musicians from Georgia (U.S state) Category:1974 births Category:Living people
